data.description: The Pullen, a 4 bed, 3.5 bath exterior townhome features an open floor plan design with plenty of light, versatile rooms and storage. The main level features a large living room, eating area, half-bath and beautiful kitchen with stainless steel sink and appliance package. Upgraded quartz countertops and kitchen island finish off this open kitchen. Combined with a large, covered outdoor living area with its own storage room and privacy wall, the Pullen is the perfect home for entertaining. [Pullen]
